  <scopecontent id="aspace_6ac2fdc9870ae607d5b86535c117229a">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Memorabilia, broadsides, photographs, and other ephemeral material from the official and alternative Stonewall 25 marches and associated cultural festival, June 25-26, 1994. Also, the video "Stonewall 25: the future is ours!," a Lefthand production for Stonewall, Inc.</p>  </scopecontent>
